- NO, IT DOESN'T.
- I WORKED FOR TERRANCE
FOR 14 YEARS.

212
00:09:34,723 --> 00:09:36,424
HE DOESN'T LIKE EASY.
HE LIKES A FIGHT.

213
00:09:36,458 --> 00:09:38,326
SO HE'S TRYING TO MAKE
ARI LOOK STUPID.

214
00:09:38,393 --> 00:09:40,094
- I DIDN'T SAY THAT.
- NO, I DID.

215
00:09:40,128 --> 00:09:42,597
HE WON'T.
YOU JUST TELL ME
IF WE WANT THIS.

216
00:09:42,631 --> 00:09:45,099
NOT FOR 100, WE DON'T.

217
00:09:46,869 --> 00:09:49,003
HI, MR. GOLD.
I'M JAKE STEINBERG.

218
00:09:49,004 --> 00:09:50,738
H.R. SENT ME UP TO REPLACE
YOUR LAST ASSISTANT.

219
00:09:50,772 --> 00:09:52,940
I DON'T CARE.
GET ME EDDIE KAPOWSKI
ON THE PHONE.

220
00:09:52,975 --> 00:09:56,177
ANY RELATION TO KELLY KAPOWSKI?
YOU KNOW, "SAVED BY THE BELL"?

221
00:09:56,211 --> 00:09:58,512
