- KAPOWSKI HERE.

224
00:10:03,852 --> 00:10:05,453
<i>It's Ari.
I got a gig for you.</i>

225
00:10:05,487 --> 00:10:07,154
TALK TO ME.

226
00:10:07,189 --> 00:10:09,757
I NEED YOU TO FIND EVERY
PIECE OF CURRENT INFORMATION

227
00:10:09,791 --> 00:10:11,292
ON TERRANCE McQUIEWICK.

228
00:10:11,326 --> 00:10:12,960
SORRY, ARI.
NO CAN DO.

229
00:10:12,995 --> 00:10:15,763
- I'VE GOT A CONFLICT.
- WHAT KIND OF CONFLICT?

230
00:10:15,797 --> 00:10:18,132
<i>- Can't say.
- DOES IT INVOLVE ME?</i>

231
00:10:18,166 --> 00:10:19,600
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

232
00:10:19,635 --> 00:10:22,236
